					<h2>Making real estate moves without a financial strategy?
</h2>				
							<ul>
							<li>
										Have you built home equity but don’t know what to do with it?
									</li>
								<li>
										Are you wondering if real estate is a smart piece of your retirement or tax plan?
									</li>
								<li>
										Is your money sitting idle when it could be multiplying your wealth?
									</li>
